Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:01.12,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx85}相聚一刻
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.16,0:00:14.98,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx85}我想打从心里大叫一句 好想快点见到你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.09,0:00:28.66,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx85}我相信总有一天 一定能相遇相知永结连理
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.94,0:00:44.01,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx85}起步走出 希望你能追着我的背影而来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.33,0:00:57.85,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx85}我孤单一人只为等候你的到来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.14,0:01:04.95,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx85}落英缤纷的春日午后
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.23,0:01:12.16,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx85}我将祈祷转为誓言
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.44,0:01:27.05,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx85}但愿你不会忘记最重要的事 永远闪亮动人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.98,0:01:26.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.22,0:01:41.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,响子,你忘了最重要的事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.49,0:01:44.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最重要的事?你指的是什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.22,0:01:46.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的心意
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.49,0:01:49.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.09,0:01:50.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢你,响子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.46,0:01:55.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从第一次见到你时,就一直…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.37,0:01:57.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在也是,以后也是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.31,0:02:07.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧,惣一郎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.52,0:02:22.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,#93 春天的预感? 两人的炽热心情!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.30,0:02:26.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可不要沮丧喔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.10,0:02:28.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们会为你举办安慰宴会的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.33,0:02:30.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会变成这样
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.90,0:02:35.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.21,0:02:37.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.05,0:02:48.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天要发表 毕业考的成绩,对不对?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.59,0:02:49.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.42,0:02:51.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要把结果告诉我哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.32,0:02:52.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当…当然
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.89,0:02:54.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.23,0:02:57.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.03,0:03:02.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还在介意他跟朱美的事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.07,0:03:06.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.64,0:03:12.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊,完蛋了,我得延毕了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.98,0:03:15.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有补考啦,别担心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.35,0:03:17.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你别事不关己说得那么轻松
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.68,0:03:20.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好不容易才找到工作耶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.52,0:03:29.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惜!别哭啊,五代
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.16,0:03:30.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有明年!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.46,0:03:32.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概就这样罗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.06,0:03:36.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是又还没确定他不能毕业
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.97,0:03:39.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过,总觉得会是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.74,0:03:41.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要我怎么回答你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.06,0:04:07.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会不会是五代打回来的?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.81,0:04:23.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦,顺利毕业啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.71,0:04:25.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊,托您的福
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.68,0:04:27.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工作找到了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.62,0:04:28.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.89,0:04:31.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想去私立幼稚园应征看看
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.66,0:04:33.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.46,0:04:36.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我帮你介绍两三家 我认识的幼稚园
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.86,0:04:38.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.44,0:04:49.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在在征人的地方很少 你别抱太大的期望
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.77,0:04:50.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.88,0:04:54.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下我会先打个电话去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.31,0:04:56.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天你可以去看看
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.18,0:04:58.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是地址和电话号码
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.08,0:05:00.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢园长
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.05,0:05:03.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么,好好加油哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.55,0:05:05.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好,那我告辞了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.56,0:05:14.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么,我就来…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.57,0:05:25.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂,来人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.88,0:05:28.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果怎么样?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.15,0:05:30.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托你的福
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.12,0:05:33.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.78,0:05:35.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.52,0:05:38.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.37,0:05:59.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好,很久没这样了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.58,0:06:04.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跌落吧,跌到深谷底吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.35,0:06:06.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永远无法翻身…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.85,0:06:12.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好奇怪哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.36,0:06:16.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂,你在干什么? 大家都在等你耶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.46,0:06:21.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这样,祝五代前途无量
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.43,0:06:22.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干杯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.73,0:06:24.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干杯!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.84,0:06:26.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,部长,恭喜你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.40,0:06:29.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要好好的给你服务一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.11,0:06:30.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我心领了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.38,0:06:34.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的没有打电话回来吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.08,0:06:35.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.98,0:06:43.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来五代果然没有合格
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.35,0:06:45.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他可能没脸回来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.42,0:06:48.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不然早就该回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.46,0:06:53.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喝吧,你也很沮丧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.40,0:06:54.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说你们啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.47,0:06:55.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.17,0:07:04.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他有喝酒喔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.81,0:07:06.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.51,0:07:08.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用再说下去没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.05,0:07:11.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种时候非得借酒浇愁不可吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.65,0:07:13.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真高兴你还肯回来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.48,0:07:15.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系,还有明年嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.99,0:07:17.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们在胡说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.16,0:07:18.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,响子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.82,0:07:20.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.32,0:07:21.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托你的福
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.03,0:07:26.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你毕业考过了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.93,0:07:27.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.67,0:07:34.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么各位,敬五代的奇蹟
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.27,0:07:36.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干杯!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.94,0:07:41.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸好我有先准备起来 (太好了,五代祝毕业)
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.08,0:07:43.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来就剩就业了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.25,0:07:45.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这才是大问题
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.62,0:07:48.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还要参加褓母考试 这次真的要举行安慰宴会了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.85,0:07:50.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用你们操心
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.26,0:07:54.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天我就要去幼稚园面试了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.66,0:07:55.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面试?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.93,0:07:59.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,椎实幼稚园的园长 帮我介绍的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.30,0:08:04.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且褓母资格考 我一定会一次就通过
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.84,0:08:06.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你蛮有自信的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.80,0:08:11.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五代,人家介绍给你的工作 你好像都没被录取过不是吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.14,0:08:13.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想得太美了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.18,0:08:16.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来你的命也真苦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.08,0:08:18.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀,我没有…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.38,0:08:20.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.36,0:08:30.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们两个不是和好了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.13,0:08:33.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是急死人了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.76,0:08:37.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一下子和好,一下子吵架 又不是小孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.67,0:08:39.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们干嘛这样看我?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.17,0:08:43.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道宾馆的事 是我惹出的风波
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.77,0:08:47.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过,这都要怪你们不干脆吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.78,0:08:49.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点发生关系吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.08,0:08:52.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他又不是你第一个男人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.82,0:08:54.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说,还是怎么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.38,0:08:57.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还无法忘记你老公吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.29,0:08:58.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朱美
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.52,0:09:00.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五代,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.96,0:09:06.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的确无法忘记惣一郎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.40,0:09:10.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是我…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.47,0:09:13.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不能因为这样就…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.81,0:09:22.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说,你喜欢五代对不对?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.42,0:09:30.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又使用缄默权吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.42,0:09:33.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寡妇就是这样才让人讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.12,0:09:36.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了一个死掉的人守贞节 有什么用呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.96,0:09:38.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.27,0:09:47.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,响…响子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.14,0:09:50.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又逃走了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.01,0:09:53.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还不是因为你欺负她
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.08,0:09:56.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为她实在太不坦率了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.51,0:10:01.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再说,我看五代这样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.69,0:10:03.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总觉得他好可怜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.13,0:10:10.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,响子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.06,0:10:18.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的确无法忘记惣一郎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.58,0:10:18.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.10,0:11:02.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五代他不要紧吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.47,0:11:04.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.41,0:11:07.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还问什么事,就是面试啊 现在应该在面试了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.04,0:11:09.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.14,0:11:13.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会不会为了昨天的事心烦 没有心情面试啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.18,0:11:17.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊,你在酒家打工?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.79,0:11:21.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊,照顾酒家小姐的小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.56,0:11:23.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来你也很辛苦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.06,0:11:26.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会啦,还好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.26,0:11:28.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么,学校能毕业吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.46,0:11:30.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的,应该没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.60,0:11:33.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外关于褓母资格的事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.27,0:11:37.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个一边工作一边考就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.27,0:11:40.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么,我会打电话通知你结果
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.41,0:11:42.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好,请多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.45,0:11:45.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我告辞了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.01,0:11:47.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.62,0:11:49.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一位请进
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.35,0:11:52.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一位面试的人不在吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.42,0:11:55.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-来了! -宏介!宏介,不要用跑的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.12,0:11:56.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安静一点
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.29,0:11:59.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很抱歉,我儿子很调皮
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.36,0:12:01.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轮到你进来面试罗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.43,0:12:03.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦,好,那么我就…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.33,0:12:04.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要,我也要
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.50,0:12:07.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行啦,爸爸要谈工作的事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.97,0:12:10.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要,我也要…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.34,0:12:13.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好,哥哥陪你玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.01,0:12:16.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很不好意思,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.51,0:12:18.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别客气,大家都是来面试的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.05,0:12:21.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来,你想玩什么呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.25,0:12:22.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当马给我骑
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.28,0:12:24.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当马给你骑?这个好难哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.45,0:12:25.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管,你要当
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.42,0:12:30.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再摇用力一点
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.17,0:12:39.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.83,0:12:41.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里,别那么说
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.67,0:12:44.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不好玩啊?宏介
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.20,0:12:48.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,普普通通 妈妈当马给我骑比较舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.28,0:12:49.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宏介!没礼貌!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.94,0:12:51.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.45,0:12:53.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.38,0:12:55.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈什么时候会回来?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.15,0:12:57.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么时候…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.86,0:13:04.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈已经是外人了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.43,0:13:07.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么?为什么?为什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.83,0:13:11.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么?我不要! 我们去接她回来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.07,0:13:13.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宏介
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.17,0:13:18.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.61,0:13:19.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.91,0:13:23.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很丢脸,我老婆跑掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.41,0:13:26.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦,别谈这个了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.48,0:13:31.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了,刚才的面试 你可能会被录取哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.29,0:13:37.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,园长一直在夸奖你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.00,0:13:46.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大男人带着一个孩子 一定很辛苦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.37,0:13:52.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被录取…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.87,0:13:57.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果找到工作的话 就能堂堂正正求婚,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.05,0:14:02.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的确无法忘记惣一郎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.30,0:14:17.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,响…响子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.13,0:14:20.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面试结果怎么样?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.60,0:14:25.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗,那个人…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.74,0:14:30.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊,不过总感觉他很可怜…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.39,0:14:44.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂,一刻馆
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.56,0:14:49.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有,他在
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.33,0:14:52.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五代 若叶幼稚园的园长打来的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.50,0:14:57.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已经到家了啊,真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.24,0:15:01.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样的 我想早点通知你比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.64,0:15:06.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才你照顾那小孩的方式 真的让我很佩服
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.11,0:15:07.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里,您太夸奖了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.45,0:15:12.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的,我相信你到任何地方 都会被录取
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.02,0:15:17.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以这次我打算录取 另外一位
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.29,0:15:21.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也知道 他带着一个小孩蛮可怜的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.36,0:15:24.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦,说…说的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.67,0:15:28.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会,好,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.44,0:15:33.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果大家的想法 好像都一样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.94,0:15:38.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我没有立场同情他
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.71,0:15:41.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过,总觉得松了一口气
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.42,0:15:44.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找工作这种事急不得
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.42,0:15:49.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能在你理想中的工作环境工作
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.36,0:15:52.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想这才是最好的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.06,0:15:54.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,响子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.57,0:16:03.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天晚上,真的很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.51,0:16:06.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惣一郎的事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.51,0:16:08.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.14,0:16:13.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我说不在意 那是骗人的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.49,0:16:19.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.20,0:16:26.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫我从心里将惣一郎抹消
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.13,0:16:30.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我或许根本办不到
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.94,0:16:35.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为他的确存在过
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.54,0:16:41.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我比任何人都爱惣一郎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.95,0:16:46.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我眼里只有惣一郎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.25,0:16:49.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追逐着惣一郎的身影
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.19,0:16:52.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惣一郎把我的心填得满满的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.46,0:16:58.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惣一郎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.87,0:17:05.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,响子,你看
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.34,0:17:08.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个断崖的地层很有意思吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.34,0:17:10.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.75,0:17:17.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时候我好幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.22,0:17:26.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许我无法给你同样的幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.00,0:17:29.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不知道该怎么说
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.00,0:17:33.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会在我能力范围内 用我的做法
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.07,0:17:39.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给你带来不同的幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.11,0:17:46.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我能做的只有这些
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.79,0:17:57.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想要同样的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.46,0:18:01.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是惣一郎的替代品
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.70,0:18:15.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂,我是音无
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.64,0:18:16.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管理员?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.70,0:18:18.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朱美?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.84,0:18:20.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不要过来?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.81,0:18:24.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在大家在茶茶丸 接续昨天的第二摊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.01,0:18:26.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听见了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.92,0:18:31.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听见了,听见了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.45,0:18:33.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我们等你来哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.62,0:18:36.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊,还有一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.06,0:18:39.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天,对不起哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.03,0:18:41.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里,我才不好意思呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.53,0:18:44.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系没关系,待会见罗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.37,0:18:50.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是朱美打来的吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.74,0:18:54.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊,叫我们去参加 昨天的第二摊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.09,0:19:06.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下雪了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.15,0:19:08.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知不觉变成下雪了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.10,0:19:24.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊,惣一郎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.01,0:19:28.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是说小狗喔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.91,0:19:32.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我还没喂它吃晚饭
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.33,0:19:51.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到你连狗的名字 都会那么在意
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.93,0:19:53.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好笑哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.10,0:19:56.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的确很好笑
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.00,0:19:58.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.77,0:20:02.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还是觉得很不安
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.84,0:20:07.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一想到你跟惣一郎的事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.18,0:20:12.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总是感到很不安
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.20,0:20:27.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经不知道该怎么办才好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.58,0:20:44.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.03,0:20:56.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求求你 除了我之外什么都别想
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.01,0:21:46.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她的心情怎么那么好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.45,0:21:48.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一之濑太太,你也那么认为吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.92,0:21:51.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起来特别开朗耶
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.55,0:21:53.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能跟五代之间 发生了什么事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.92,0:21:55.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁知道
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.12,0:21:58.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五代到哪里去了?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.59,0:22:00.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,医院
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.26,0:22:02.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,医院?他哪里不舒服吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.80,0:22:06.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他好像说要去探病
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.80,0:22:11.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正式录用?您的意思是?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.84,0:22:14.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我闪到了腰
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.71,0:22:16.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能年纪大了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.34,0:22:19.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加上幼稚园只有我一个男人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.65,0:22:21.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.62,0:22:25.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好,我才要请您多多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.09,0:22:27.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我找到工作了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.26,0:22:31.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.33,0:22:34.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他好像找到工作了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.50,0:22:37.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上次那些还有剩哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.03,0:22:41.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了,真的太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.04,0:22:45.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你,真的…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.71,0:22:51.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…响子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.44,0:22:52.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.08,0:22:59.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请你跟我…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.56,0:23:04.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜你!五代!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.23,0:23:09.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起,我没听到…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.93,0:23:12.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀,挂断了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.40,0:23:20.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.38,0:23:25.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,响子
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.48,0:23:32.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请你跟我结婚
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.59,0:23:41.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜你,五代
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.43,0:23:41.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.94,0:23:52.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五代求婚了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.18,0:23:55.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没,虽然他昨晚也练习了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.08,0:23:58.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过,听说管理员的爸爸极力反对
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.29,0:24:00.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还冲去酒家找他呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.49,0:24:04.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相聚一刻下一回 “太好了!五代决死的求婚”
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.19,0:24:07.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,响子,请你跟我结婚
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.32,0:24:07.32,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.98,0:24:15.71,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx88}Begin the night Begin your love
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.99,0:24:28.64,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx88}你该知道这不是擦身而过的恋情 亲吻也是…woo
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.17,0:24:46.66,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx88}你比我想像中冷淡 喜欢一个人独处 沉默不语
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.94,0:24:57.42,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx88}不要逞强 在这烛火依偎着的夜晚
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.83,0:25:14.85,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx88}凝视着你的一切 试着将至今的谎言吹熄
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.55,0:25:22.11,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx88}Begin the night Begin your love
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.39,0:25:34.50,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx88}自我陶醉故弄玄虚 对我行不通…woo

